                                        <tr class="biblio-image-tile tr-striped"><td class="col-sm-3">
                                            <a id="img-1532206-img131603" data-pos="last" href="#modal-image" data-modal-toggle="true" class="biblio-image-tile-a ga-click-event apporder order title desc" data-imgid="1532206-img131603" data-lityx data-category="Extracted Images" data-label="biblio: image thumbnail" data-value="1532206-img131603" data-apporder="p. 24" data-order="7" data-imgid="1532206-img131603" data-imgsrc="/biblio/1532206/image/001/522/0015228/1/0131603.png" data-title="Figure 6" data-desc="&lt;em&gt;(a) Measured scattering curves from pH 12.30 (top) to pH 2.91 (bottom), and (b) corresponding titration curve for DVB-PS-PMAA series in water.&lt;/em&gt; Black solid lines are fits to the GCEV model, with the parameters given in Table S5. The insert depicts the measured Guinier R&lt;sub&gt;G&lt;/sub&gt; for the 100% acidic series as a function of pH. The outer block is PMAA (blue with x=30); see Figure 1 caption for other details." data-ostiid="1532206">
